txt.en: Wights can be found in Emyn Duir.\n\nYou should defeat wights.
A bounty notice has asked you to drive the wights out of Emyn Duir.
You have defeated many wights in Emyn Duir, and the one who posted the bounty is certain to be pleased.

The bounty notice reads:

'These lands have no shortage of foul creatures, but if you ask me the wight is the worst, bedraggled and disgusting. They are beasts of horror, and I hesitate to call them something so common as pests, but they harass our gravesites and bother our dead. It turns my stomach to think of them!

'If you wish to earn some coin and have the time to spare, I implore you to hunt as many of the vile creatures as you can. I am sick of the things!'
